Package: uccdf
Type: Package
Title: Typed Consensus Clustering for Structured Data Frames
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Dai",
      family = "Dai",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "daik54015@gmail.com"
    )
  )
Description: Provides a typed consensus clustering workflow for structured
    mixed-type data frames. The package validates tabular input, infers a
    simple schema, builds a mixed-distance view and a mixed-latent view,
    aggregates clustering results across resamples and learners, and applies
    null-calibrated K selection with confidence and ambiguity summaries.
    It is designed for practical exploratory clustering workflows that need
    stable assignments, transparent diagnostics, and a compact API.
URL: https://dai540.github.io/uccdf/,
    https://github.com/dai540/uccdf
